Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------------------INTRO-------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺…刺下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人了…是我…杀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连人都不敢杀  还拿什么剑  你这个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂娅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------------------APART-------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂娅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂娅  感觉好点了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗  蒂娅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤势如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不巧  这里没有会使用治愈术的第七音谱术士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您的关心  大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己能治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了的说  太好了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道你不是军人  却没能去理解你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为军人  保护人民是我的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若因此而负伤  说明是我无能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  两位感情那么好  真让人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  配合也很默契啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂娅和主人的脸都通红的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  蒂娅既然没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不是该早点出发了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮丝有音讯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  有她的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给亲爱的杰德大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然遇到了很可怕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总算到达第二地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个很重要的东西也在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表扬我吧表扬我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮丝最~~喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好害羞  人家告白了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克大人没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非~常担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想早点见到卢克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便也请照顾好伊昂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮丝上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  卢克先生你真受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二地点是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指在国境线上的凯茨尔军港
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来  要渡过弗布拉斯河啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  凯明明是基姆拉斯卡人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却对马尔库特的地形很熟悉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兴趣是桌上旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了凯茨尔就能和梵谣将合流了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见到师傅？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他…
